{"tid":1867633,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"就算社區爆發，醫護都要繼續罷工，直至完全封關","createTime":"2020-02-07T09:00:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-07T09:14:13.000Z","uid":79559,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"afd92cd23f70eb24fa93bb50d2e83f16556d76fc","tid":1867633,"uid":79559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T09:00:50.000Z","msg":"雖然唔知今日表決結果，但好想比HAEA知，好多人好想佢哋可以堅持，唔好咁易放棄呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然社區爆發係真攬炒，但原因係政府唔肯完全封關又慢動作推出19政策做成。知你哋承受好多壓力，被冷處理，中傷同抹黑，但好想比你哋知好多人明白同撐你哋。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他行業既人，有工會就入工會，團結先有力量，香港人冇幾多時間可以自救。<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n少少意見：<br />\n唔洗靠垃圾醫管局回應，仆街高層只會拖；企硬你哋既條件，比哂責任對家，佢哋滿足到先有理由同佢哋傾。希望你哋睇到，堅持罷工到底<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0af5769b04687192cdf6dd89fd9760159618b154","tid":1867633,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T09:01:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d4a535ed987fff821900f9d77d53724aa26d9d9","tid":1867633,"uid":79559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T09:02:15.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79245e796940a27c5b962910dc8313ba9453f80e","tid":1867633,"uid":285371,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T09:02:35.000Z","msg":"「我本人僅此聲明，就算社區爆發，依然支持醫護繼續罷工，直至政府落實封關及其它訴求！」<br />\n<br />\n只要所有公民社會嘅個體都咁做，HAEA嘅人睇到，或者會回心轉意，堅持罷工到底"},{"pid":"52607f6cc717f93d704b76eeb8b0e142867cfb92","tid":1867633,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T09:03:14.000Z","msg":"唔好再口頭罷工喇慷他人之慨無意思"},{"pid":"0385deb2a198bba7a3397b1d957713331a4eaf82","tid":1867633,"uid":201826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T09:05:13.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"34611a5ef4f7d458230cb5b7004fe52336a6d9e0","tid":1867633,"uid":62469,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T09:06:30.000Z","msg":"其他人都要罷先有用"},{"pid":"5be2d8d8b596fe529137008e824808d954d9d677","tid":1867633,"uid":40521,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T09:07:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/OGJOBMw.png\" />"},{"pid":"4c9279ab044721ccb2384bbbd891757ed52dbd7c","tid":1867633,"uid":269061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T09:14:13.000Z","msg":"醫護<br />\n<br />\n投票時間至1800🟥<br />\n<br />\n要6000會員投票呀‼️‼️‼️‼️<br />\n快啲出黎啦‼️‼️‼️<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n【延長醫護罷工計劃投票】<br />\n投票截至今日下午六時<br />\n只限會員<br />\n￼<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSf_VSITn5RwMPGSP36LWB06DYnns4wnLlsHi2-PBumry03GHw/viewform\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSf_VSITn5RwMPGSP36LWB06DYnns4wnLlsHi2-PBumry03GHw%2Fviewform&d=uFnVTFPFhHj2sSFH0VdWwbeFZk%2BLn%2Bp4m9s6a9hK%2BPA%3D&h=d774e221\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSf_VSITn5RwMPGSP36LWB06DYnns4wnLlsHi2-PBumry03GHw/viewform</a>"}]}